tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE recommendations (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    rating FLOAT,
    last_interaction TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_profile (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    email VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE user_preferences (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    preference1 VARCHAR(100),
    preference2 VARCHAR(100),
    preference3 VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE user_behavior (
    user_id INT,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
CREATE TABLE users (user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, username VARCHAR(255), email VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE products (product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL);

CREATE TABLE user_purchases (purchase_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID, product_id UUID, purchase_date TIMESTAMP, FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id), FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id));
CREATE TABLE user_preferences (user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, preference_1 VARCHAR(255), preference_2 VARCHAR(255), preference_3 VARCHAR(255));

CREATE TABLE recommendations (recommendation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID, product_id UUID, recommendation_score DECIMAL, FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id), FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id));
